11 (B) (1) A CONSUMER REPORTING AGENCY MAY NOT:
12 (I) MAKE, CREATE, OR FURNISH ANY CONSUMER REPORT
13 CONTAINING, INCORPORATING, OR REFLECTING:
14 1. ANY ADVERSE INFORMATION THAT THE CONSUMER
