27 (C) A PERSON MAY NOT USE MEDICAL DEBT INFORMATION INCLUDED IN A
28 CONSUMER REPORT TO MAKE A DETERMINATION REGARDING THE
29 CREDITWORTHINESS OF THE CONSUMER.
